:#  Notes								      *
:#									      *
:#  History	                                                              *
:#   2010-04-07 JFL Created this batch.                                       *
:#   2017-03-01 JFL Streamlined the code.                                     *
:#   2017-03-02 JFL Added VERSION and option -V.                              *
:#   2017-03-03 JFL Output two distinct variables: OBJECTS and PLUSOBJS       *
